description: Lists all endpoints associated with an Outpost that has been shared by Amazon Web Services Resource Access Manager (RAM). Related actions include:

parameters.name: OutpostId
parameters.description: The ID of the Amazon Web Services Outpost.

nested_items.name: Endpoints
nested_items.description: The list of endpoints associated with the specified Outpost that have been shared by Amazon Web Services Resource Access Manager (RAM).

nested_items.name: EndpointArn
nested_items.description: The Amazon Resource Name (ARN) of the endpoint.

nested_items.name: CidrBlock
nested_items.description: The VPC CIDR committed by this endpoint.

nested_items.name: CreationTime
nested_items.description: The time the endpoint was created.

nested_items.name: NetworkInterfaces
nested_items.description: The network interface of the endpoint.

nested_items.name: NetworkInterfaceId
nested_items.description: The ID for the network interface.

nested_items.name: VpcId
nested_items.description: The ID of the VPC used for the endpoint.

nested_items.name: SubnetId
nested_items.description: The ID of the subnet used for the endpoint.

nested_items.name: SecurityGroupId
nested_items.description: The ID of the security group used for the endpoint.

nested_items.name: AccessType
nested_items.description: The type of connectivity used to access the Amazon S3 on Outposts endpoint.

nested_items.name: CustomerOwnedIpv4Pool
nested_items.description: The ID of the customer-owned IPv4 address pool used for the endpoint.

nested_items.name: FailedReason
nested_items.description: The failure reason, if any, for a create or delete endpoint operation.

nested_items.name: ErrorCode
nested_items.description: The failure code, if any, for a create or delete endpoint operation.

nested_items.name: Message
nested_items.description: Additional error details describing the endpoint failure and recommended action.

nested_items.name: NextToken
nested_items.description: If the number of endpoints associated with the specified Outpost exceeds MaxResults, you can include this value in subsequent calls to this operation to retrieve more results.
